---
import { profiles, engines } from "../data/profiles";
---

<section id="profili" class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20 sm:py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-400">Il concetto che cambia tutto</p>
    <h2 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-50 sm:text-4xl">
      7 profili di tracciamento, 6 motori di calcolo
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-zinc-400">
      Ogni prodotto sceglie come essere contato. Varasto applica il motore giusto — dallo sfuso ai
      seriali, dai lotti ai deperibili — così le giacenze sono sempre corrette.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-14 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
    {
      profiles.map((p) => (
        <div class="group rounded-xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-zinc-900/50 p-5 transition hover:border-indigo-500/30 hover:bg-zinc-900">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-500/10 text-sm font-bold text-indigo-400">
              {p.n}
            </span>
            <span class="rounded-md border border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.02] px-2 py-0.5 font-mono text-[10px] text-zinc-500">
              {p.engine}
            </span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 font-semibold text-zinc-100">{p.name}</h3>
          <p class="mt-1.5 text-sm text-zinc-400">{p.desc}</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-zinc-600">Es. {p.examples}</p>
        </div>
      ))
    }
  </div>

  <p class="mt-8 text-center font-mono text-xs text-zinc-600">
    Motori · {engines.join(" · ")}
  </p>
</section>
